commit 63c7ecaf6423549f093c85de656af5aaaa80c175
Author: nosman <stephanos.tsoucas@gmail.com>
Date:   Sun Apr 5 19:13:11 2026 -0400

    Improve VS Code extension UX: search highlights, minimize panel, SCM colors

    - Search results show matching snippet as label instead of session name
    - Opening a session from search highlights matched terms and scrolls to first hit
    - Tool use groups with search hits auto-expand and highlight matching content
    - Session detail opens at bottom so new messages are visible immediately
    - Session detail tabs open in column 1 (left of main Gossamer panel)
    - Main Gossamer panel is minimizable (Ctrl+K G toggle, server stays alive)
    - Ctrl+K Ctrl+G focuses the checkpoints sidebar
    - Checkpoint file tree uses resourceUri with absolute paths for SCM color decorations

    Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
    Entire-Checkpoint: 41096d310d44

